 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; might want to specify these MCA params in the default MCA<br>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; param file, or the environment, ...etc. &nbsp;Just so that you<br>
 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; don&#39;t have to specify it on every mpirun command line.<br>
